Program: Outlook
Title: The Kidnap of Shawn Hornbeck
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrtr
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Shawn Hornbeck's parents talk about his kidnapping and 4 years in captivity. Also, finding India's young entrepreneur of the year; Catherine Lucas talks about her book 'Carry Me Home'; a look at the Bnei Menashe, and their claims as a lost tribe of Israel living in Manipur, India. Presenter: Frederick Dove. Show less